title: Teemoing minigame icon
body: Hi I completed the minigame where I had to sacrifice 500 cute little minios about 3 days ago but I still didnt receive the scared minion icon. Do I have to wait or is it a problem? Sorry for my bad english.

replies.body:
The [Teemoing Official page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016) mentions it can take some time to get the Icon on your account:

>**Icons will be granted up to two weeks after November 3, 2016 at 23:59 PT.**

Let me know if you have any other questions.
